python第三方模块 

	> pip install 模块名称  
	
python虚拟环境 

	隔离


1、创建虚拟环境 

> python -m venv 虚拟环境名称 

C:\Users\martin>d:
D:\>python -m venv test1
D:\>python -m venv test2


2、进入test1环境，安装requests模块 

D:\>cd test1
D:\test1>cd Scripts
D:\test1\Scripts>activate

(test1) D:\>cd test1
(test1) D:\test1>cd Scripts
(test1) D:\test1\Scripts>pip install requests


3、退出python虚拟环境  

(test1) D:\test1\Scripts>deactivate



